        "symbol": "RGAS.TA",
        "sector": "Industrials",
        "industry": "Waste Management",
        "description": "R.G.A. Services & Cleaning (Israel) 1987 Ltd provides various services to the public works, sanitation, and environmental quality departments in municipal authorities. It specializes in street cleaning, mechanical sweepers, public institutions, educational institutions, public transportation, government institutions, and garbage and debris removal services for local authorities. It offers its services to local authorities and institutions in Israel, including Tiberias, Hadera, Netanya, Ramat Hasharon, Ramat Gan, Holon, Tel Aviv, Rishon LeZion, Ramla, Bat Yam, Kfar Saba, Beer Sheva, Jerusalem, Herzliya, Bnei Brak, Holon, and others. The company was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Giv'at Shmuel, Israel. As of February 6, 2025, R.G.A. Services & Cleaning (Israel) 1987 Ltd operates as a subsidiary of Value Capital One Ltd.",
